Description_lang: Arcanotron launches an arcane bomb at a nearby location. If the bomb strikes the ground, it explodes, inflicting $470012s1 Arcane damage to all players.If the bomb strikes a player it inflicts $470020s1 Arcane damage, increases the player's arcane damage taken by $470020s2% for $470020d, and Arcanotron launches another bomb that will strike the ground more quickly.Arcane Overcharge will inflict less damage to the raid for each bomb that was caught.
